    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Edward Hines Jr. VA Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if using a nutritionally enhanced supplement will improve mucositis in head and
      neck cancer patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      H&amp;N cancer patients will be randomized to receive either a nutritionally enhanced product or
      standard treatment. The patients in both groups will receive nutritional counseling weekly by
      the RD. Anthropometric measures, available lab values, mucositis grade, and quality of life
      measures will be compared between groups.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
